<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，有一个小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他住在一个安静的村庄里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村子里的人都有羊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿的工作就是放羊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他要保护羊群不被狼吃掉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>放羊很简单，但是一点儿意思也没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真无聊！”小男孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想来点儿刺激的东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，小男孩儿有了一个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他深深地吸了一口气，张开嘴大喊：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼来了！狼来了！救命啊！狼来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个村庄都听到了小男孩儿的喊声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们停下了手上的工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65757</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村子里的人向小男孩儿跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼在哪儿？狼在哪儿？”一位老人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“羊群没事吗？”一位妇人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，狼没有来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿捉弄了大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村子里的人都很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，小男孩儿又在放羊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天真有意思。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还想玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿深深地吸了一口气，大声喊道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼来了！一只又大又吓人的狼！狼来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿的叫声又大又清晰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都停下了手上的工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跑向小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼在哪儿？”那位老人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，当然没有狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿又一次捉弄了大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果没有狼，就别喊狼！”他们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天傍晚，小男孩儿准备要回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他听到奇怪的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是一只狼！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿深深地吸了一口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用尽全力大声地喊：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼来了！一只大狼！救命啊！狼来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都听到了小男孩儿的叫喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们以为他又在搞恶作剧，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以没有人理他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼追赶并吃掉了羊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，村里的人都出来寻找小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“羊呢？发生什么事了？”妇人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼来了！我大声叫喊，但是没有人来！”小男孩儿喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当你前两次说‘狼来了’的时候，狼真的来了吗？”老人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”小男孩儿尴尬地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么为什么当你真的看到狼的时候，我们要相信你？”老人训斥道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人会相信说谎的人，即使他说的是实话！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>